cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting physCellId to a negative value (-1) will cause invalid physical cell ID configuration and cell identification failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 physCellId 設定為負值 (-1)，會導致無效的物理小區 ID 配置，並造成小區識別失敗。
